## Query Parameters

**search_name** (string, REQUIRED)
- Name of person, company, or entity to search
- Can be partial name (database will fuzzy match)
- Examples: "Vladimir Putin", "Mossack Fonseca", "Apple Inc"
- Tips:
  - Use full name for people ("John Smith" not "Smith")
  - Use company legal name if known
  - Database handles variations and aliases

**entity_type** (string, REQUIRED)
- Type of offshore entity to search for
- Values: **"Officer"**, **"Entity"**, **"Address"**, **"Intermediary"**, **"All"**
- Guidance:
  - **"Officer"** - Searching for a PERSON (politician, CEO, individual)
  - **"Entity"** - Searching for a COMPANY/TRUST (shell company, offshore corporation)
  - **"Intermediary"** - Searching for LAW FIRM/BANK (who set up the structures)
  - **"Address"** - Searching by LOCATION (specific offshore address)
  - **"All"** - Search all types (use when unsure or want comprehensive results)

**jurisdiction** (string, can be empty "")
- Country/jurisdiction to filter results by
- Common offshore jurisdictions:
  - "British Virgin Islands" (BVI) - Most common tax haven
  - "Panama" - Panama Papers source
  - "Cayman Islands" - Major offshore financial center
  - "Bermuda" - Insurance and reinsurance haven
  - "Bahamas" - Banking secrecy
  - "Switzerland" - Banking secrecy
  - "Luxembourg" - European tax haven
  - "Cyprus" - Russian money flows
  - "Seychelles" - Growing tax haven
  - "Malta" - EU tax haven
- Leave empty ("") to search all jurisdictions

**leak_source** (string, can be empty "")
- Specific leak investigation to search within
- Values: "Panama Papers", "Paradise Papers", "Pandora Papers", "Bahamas Leaks", "Offshore Leaks"
- Leave empty ("") to search ALL leaks (recommended unless question specifies)

